          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used in private or public recitation and prayer in praise of Welfare (Maṅgala), personified as a deity and given various epithets such as "the remover of debt" (ṛṇaharta), "giver of money" (dhanaprada), and the like.</summary>
            <textLang>In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Maṅgalastotra</title>
              <colophon>Colophon: it[i] śrīskaṃdapurāṇe kāśīkhaṃḍe maṃgalastotraṃ saṃpūrṇāṃ // śrīsāṃbasadāśivārpaṇam astu // (f. 2r).</colophon>
